301
00:17:05,720 --> 00:17:07,480
Even an asshole like me

302
00:17:07,480 --> 00:17:08,840
has nightmares at night.

303
00:17:10,240 --> 00:17:12,440
Seeing as how I'm capable

304
00:17:12,440 --> 00:17:13,800
to lead an army and fight wars,

305
00:17:14,200 --> 00:17:15,640
it's better to just serve the country.

306
00:17:17,280 --> 00:17:19,440
You have the world in your heart.

307
00:17:19,880 --> 00:17:22,080
I am

308
00:17:22,080 --> 00:17:22,960
inferior to you.

309
00:17:27,500 --> 00:17:29,240
You're making me blush.

310
00:17:35,424 --> 00:17:36,480
This way.

311
00:17:36,480 --> 00:17:38,020
Young Master!

312
00:17:38,600 --> 00:17:40,080
Young Master, careful.

313
00:17:40,080 --> 00:17:41,050
What's wrong?

314
00:17:41,800 --> 00:17:43,400
Look.

