317
00:17:45,880 --> 00:17:48,120
All of them want to come here and visit you,

318
00:17:48,120 --> 00:17:49,120
Commander.

319
00:17:49,300 --> 00:17:51,600
I couldn't even drive them away.

320
00:17:51,680 --> 00:17:52,480
Lord Sheng.

321
00:17:52,480 --> 00:17:54,025
It's the state mourning period

322
00:17:54,040 --> 00:17:55,160
and yet they all are coming?

323
00:17:57,920 --> 00:18:00,000
All of them want to marry their daughters to me.

324
00:18:01,400 --> 00:18:03,240
It's still the state mourning period.

325
00:18:04,800 --> 00:18:06,400
These people

326
00:18:06,400 --> 00:18:07,080
don't care about

327
00:18:07,080 --> 00:18:09,000
the state mourning.

328
00:18:10,600 --> 00:18:11,840
A few days ago

329
00:18:11,840 --> 00:18:13,080
on the doorstep of Fan House,

330
00:18:13,080 --> 00:18:14,320
