331
00:18:15,240 --> 00:18:16,320
They insisted

332
00:18:16,320 --> 00:18:17,050
they had a marriage alliance with me

333
00:18:17,050 --> 00:18:17,840
when I was little!

334
00:18:18,100 --> 00:18:19,360
They even grabbed Rong

335
00:18:19,360 --> 00:18:21,240
