336
00:18:21,560 --> 00:18:24,040
That really scared me!

337
00:18:24,040 --> 00:18:25,280
I hurriedly carried Rong off and left.

338
00:18:25,400 --> 00:18:26,720
I said that I was going to the lavatory.

339
00:18:29,000 --> 00:18:30,160
What?

340
00:18:30,160 --> 00:18:31,920
You didn't like any of them?

341
00:18:36,440 --> 00:18:37,680
Why doesn't your Sheng Family

342
00:18:38,200 --> 00:18:40,800
recommend a daughter

343
00:18:40,800 --> 00:18:42,160
to be my wife?

344
00:18:42,200 --> 00:18:43,440
Dream on!

345
00:18:44,680 --> 00:18:45,640
My mother

346
00:18:46,440 --> 00:18:47,640
has long set her eyes

347
00:18:47,640 --> 00:18:49,080
on the son of my uncle

348
00:18:49,080 --> 00:18:50,080
to be my Fifth Little Sister's husband.

349
00:18:51,120 --> 00:18:52,400
For Sixth Little Sister,

350
00:18:52,400 --> 00:18:54,200
it's of course Grandmother's call.

351
00:18:54,920 --> 00:18:56,625
She seems to have set her eyes

352
00:18:56,640 --> 00:18:57,650
on the youngest son

353
00:18:57,650 --> 00:18:58,840
of the House of He from Baishitan.

354
00:19:00,760 --> 00:19:03,440
The House of He who are doctors by profession?

