But it seems to be more or less settled.

361
00:19:15,500 --> 00:19:16,640
I've also seen him.

362
00:19:17,800 --> 00:19:19,880
That lad from the House of He

363
00:19:19,880 --> 00:19:23,520
is gentle and honest.

364
00:19:24,160 --> 00:19:25,480
Sixth Little Sister

365
00:19:25,480 --> 00:19:28,120
has a good character and taste.

366
00:19:28,500 --> 00:19:29,880
