380
00:20:16,360 --> 00:20:18,560
You must always be careful.

381
00:20:19,240 --> 00:20:20,120
I know.

382
00:20:20,880 --> 00:20:22,400
The only thing that worries me is

383
00:20:22,400 --> 00:20:23,680
