384
00:20:25,680 --> 00:20:26,875
I've already informed my brothers

385
00:20:26,875 --> 00:20:27,440
in the Canal Gang

386
00:20:27,440 --> 00:20:28,400
to search for him in Jiangnan.

387
00:20:31,240 --> 00:20:32,480
Anyway,

388
00:20:32,480 --> 00:20:33,075
if there is any news,

389
00:20:33,075 --> 00:20:34,000
they will send it to the capital.

390
00:20:34,040 --> 00:20:36,200
Help me look out for it.

391
00:20:36,200 --> 00:20:38,040
Your son is my nephew.

392
00:20:38,040 --> 00:20:39,280
I surely will be mindful about it.

393
00:20:40,280 --> 00:20:42,640
Thank you for your trouble, Young Master Sheng.

394
00:20:43,800 --> 00:20:45,680
