00:21:07,200 --> 00:21:08,280
I know!

406
00:21:08,280 --> 00:21:10,320
I don't like any of those families!

407
00:21:11,760 --> 00:21:14,360
Your Master!

408
00:21:14,720 --> 00:21:16,520
Could it be that you already like someone?

409
00:21:17,720 --> 00:21:18,960
Go back! All of you, just go back!

410
00:21:50,960 --> 00:21:51,680
Shitou.

411
00:21:54,280 --> 00:21:56,080
I want to ask you to do something for me.

412
00:21:56,640 --> 00:21:57,880
The battlefield is so dangerous.

