00:22:00,480 --> 00:22:02,520
I'm only at ease if you're the one

415
00:22:02,560 --> 00:22:03,520
who handles this matter for me.

416
00:22:35,720 --> 00:22:36,760
Miss,

417
00:22:36,760 --> 00:22:37,850
the osmanthus flower harvest this year

418
00:22:37,850 --> 00:22:38,320
is really great.

419
00:22:38,560 --> 00:22:40,080
After air-drying, there is still so much left.

420
00:22:40,080 --> 00:22:41,320
They're cleaner than the ones being sold outside!

421
00:22:42,480 --> 00:22:43,360
Really?

422
00:22:45,200 --> 00:22:46,760
Salt-preserve and then fry them.

423
00:22:46,760 --> 00:22:47,840
Xiaotao loves eating most.

424
00:22:48,680 --> 00:22:49,760
Miss,

425
00:22:49,760 --> 00:22:51,320
