426
00:22:53,200 --> 00:22:54,680
We feel as if the days are passing by so quickly,

427
00:22:55,000 --> 00:22:55,800
but Miss instead might be feeling

428
00:22:55,840 --> 00:22:56,920
as if the days are years.

429
00:22:57,200 --> 00:22:59,240
So wanting the state mourning to be over,

430
00:22:59,240 --> 00:23:00,280
so the He Family can come and propose marriage.

