00:23:01,000 --> 00:23:03,040
You girl, you're becoming more and more unruly.

432
00:23:03,040 --> 00:23:03,840
What nonsense are you saying?

433
00:23:04,200 --> 00:23:04,840
If anyone hears it,

434
00:23:04,840 --> 00:23:06,320
