435
00:23:07,560 --> 00:23:08,800
This marriage

436
00:23:08,800 --> 00:23:09,560
is already

437
00:23:09,560 --> 00:23:10,360
a sure thing.

438
00:23:10,840 --> 00:23:12,280
Only the betrothal gifts are left to seal it.

439
00:23:12,560 --> 00:23:14,280
Miss, don't be shy.

440
00:23:14,800 --> 00:23:15,840
Indeed.

441
00:23:16,080 --> 00:23:17,520
Look at those mandarin ducks playing in the water

442
00:23:17,520 --> 00:23:18,280
and hundred of butterflies over the flowers.

443
00:23:18,550 --> 00:23:19,640
Her embroidery is all about

444
00:23:19,640 --> 00:23:20,920
a harmonious married couple's life.

445
00:23:23,040 --> 00:23:23,625
If I don't embroider that,

446
00:23:23,625 --> 00:23:24,160
what should I embroider?

447
00:23:24,640 --> 00:23:25,440
Do you want me

448
00:23:25,440 --> 00:23:26,800
to embroider steamed herring

449
00:23:26,800 --> 00:23:28,480
and rose flaky pastry instead?

450
00:23:28,840 --> 00:23:30,560
You might be happy,

451
00:23:30,560 --> 00:23:32,040
but I'll get beaten out of here!

452
00:23:34,040 --> 00:23:36,280
Greetings, Sixth Miss.

453
00:23:36,280 --> 00:23:37,480
Young Lord He is here.

454
00:23:37,480 --> 00:23:38,075
He's with Old Madam

455
00:23:38,075 --> 00:23:39,200
and waiting for the meal to be served.

456
00:23:39,200 --> 00:23:41,000
Old Madam said that she is tired.

457
00:23:41,120 --> 00:23:42,200
She asked that you go there,

458
00:23:42,200 --> 00:23:43,040
and chat with him a little.

459
00:23:44,760 --> 00:23:45,960
Okay, I got it.

460
00:23:46,960 --> 00:23:47,880
And we were just talking about him.

461
00:23:47,880 --> 00:23:48,800
He is over here.

462
00:23:49,200 --> 00:23:50,680
I don't want to defy the mandate of heaven!

463
00:23:58,280 --> 00:23:59,475
I was delivering medicinal ingredients

464
00:23:59,475 --> 00:24:00,000
outside recently,

465
00:24:00,600 --> 00:24:01,325
and it happened to coincide

466
00:24:01,325 --> 00:24:02,120
with the return of my Uncle Cao

467
00:24:02,160 --> 00:24:03,720
from the borders after being given a pardon.

468
00:24:04,040 --> 00:24:05,720
