470
00:24:07,840 --> 00:24:09,480
Hope Old Madam didn't mind.

471
00:24:10,600 --> 00:24:12,360
Having a good business is a more important matter.

472
00:24:13,040 --> 00:24:15,320
It's also proper to help your relatives out.

473
00:24:16,200 --> 00:24:17,680
Hong, you don't need to blame yourself.

474
00:24:18,880 --> 00:24:20,440
It's not also self-blaming.

475
00:24:20,440 --> 00:24:22,280
I'm just eager to visit you, Old Madam.

476
00:24:24,200 --> 00:24:26,800
Look how honeymouthed this child is.

477
00:24:26,800 --> 00:24:27,746
Indeed.

478
00:24:30,480 --> 00:24:31,920
The weather is slowly getting colder.

479
00:24:31,920 --> 00:24:33,320
Little Sister has to greet Old Madam

480
00:24:33,320 --> 00:24:34,680
