481
00:24:34,800 --> 00:24:36,360
You must wear more clothing.

482
00:24:36,360 --> 00:24:37,880
Regarding food, don't be greedy for cold dishes.

483
00:24:38,280 --> 00:24:39,160
You must be

484
00:24:39,160 --> 00:24:40,320
extra careful.

485
00:24:41,800 --> 00:24:43,640
Why don't you just directly say

486
00:24:43,640 --> 00:24:45,040
that I shouldn't be a glutton.

487
00:24:47,320 --> 00:24:48,680
A good appetite is a blessing.

488
00:24:48,680 --> 00:24:50,520
This way, our body can be healthy.

489
00:24:50,800 --> 00:24:52,840
When Mother returned from our hometown this time

490
00:24:52,840 --> 00:24:54,280
