00:25:26,400 --> 00:25:27,880
Last month,

505
00:25:27,880 --> 00:25:29,360
when the whole family of Auntie Cao returned,

506
00:25:30,040 --> 00:25:31,400
Mother was so happy

507
00:25:31,400 --> 00:25:32,375
that her health has become better

508
00:25:32,375 --> 00:25:33,000
than earlier this year.

509
00:25:33,880 --> 00:25:36,160
Your mother has poor health.

510
00:25:36,160 --> 00:25:37,320
I'm also a sickly person.

511
00:25:38,240 --> 00:25:39,650
As they say, if you're chronically ill,

512
00:25:39,650 --> 00:25:40,840
