513
00:25:40,840 --> 00:25:41,500
Plus the fact that

514
00:25:41,500 --> 00:25:42,560
I have such a gluttonous granddaughter,

515
00:25:43,000 --> 00:25:44,760
we've come up with

516
00:25:44,760 --> 00:25:46,240
a medicinal dish recipe.

517
00:25:46,720 --> 00:25:47,925
We want to gift it to your mother

518
00:25:47,925 --> 00:25:49,280
to nourish her health.

519
00:25:51,000 --> 00:25:52,520
Your family has been doctors for generations.

520
00:25:53,550 --> 00:25:54,775
We are just displaying our slight skills

521
00:25:54,775 --> 00:25:55,740
before an expert.

522
00:25:56,760 --> 00:25:58,040
You and your grandmother

523
00:25:58,240 --> 00:25:59,875
