525
00:26:02,600 --> 00:26:04,160
I am only be grateful to Old Madam

526
00:26:04,440 --> 00:26:06,080
and Sixth Miss.

527
00:26:06,080 --> 00:26:08,700
I dare not think too highly of myself.

528
00:26:08,700 --> 00:26:09,900
Sit. Sit down!

529
00:26:18,240 --> 00:26:20,480
This recipe book of medicinal dishes of Sixth Miss

530
00:26:20,480 --> 00:26:21,150
surely will have both

531
00:26:21,150 --> 00:26:22,200
