532
00:26:22,520 --> 00:26:23,360
I surely must

533
00:26:23,360 --> 00:26:24,491
read this carefully when I go back.

534
00:26:25,400 --> 00:26:26,075
A ruler and his subjects assist each other,

535
00:26:26,475 --> 00:26:27,120
can help each other out.

536
00:26:27,360 --> 00:26:28,575
She might want to leave her name

537
00:26:28,575 --> 00:26:29,400
in the medicinal books.

538
00:26:31,320 --> 00:26:32,800
You're praising our Miss so much.

539
00:26:32,960 --> 00:26:34,160
Can she have better medical skills

540
00:26:34,160 --> 00:26:34,960
than you?

541
00:26:35,720 --> 00:26:36,920
She is very talented.

542
00:26:37,240 --> 00:26:38,560
