00:27:07,560 --> 00:27:08,200
Seeing Young Master He

553
00:27:08,200 --> 00:27:09,240
is so good with our Miss,

554
00:27:09,760 --> 00:27:10,880
I'm at ease.

555
00:27:10,880 --> 00:27:11,960
Our Miss will surely

