559
00:27:17,800 --> 00:27:18,480
Cousin!

560
00:27:19,880 --> 00:27:21,600
Cousin Hongwen!

561
00:27:21,600 --> 00:27:22,240
Cousin!

562
00:27:22,400 --> 00:27:23,040
Who is that?

