00:40:25,000 --> 00:40:26,000
Is that true?

863
00:40:30,040 --> 00:40:30,600
Then you . . .

864
00:40:30,600 --> 00:40:31,040
Fifth sister.

865
00:40:31,040 --> 00:40:32,000
What are you doing here?

866
00:40:32,160 --> 00:40:34,240
I ate too much too and came to digest.

867
00:40:34,662 --> 00:40:35,320
Good.

868
00:40:35,600 --> 00:40:36,700
Then I'm going back to my room.

869
00:40:36,720 --> 00:40:37,860
Please do not go back to home.

870
00:40:38,000 --> 00:40:39,360
Teach me some needlework.

871
00:40:39,360 --> 00:40:40,120
Come to my room.

872
00:40:40,120 --> 00:40:41,560
Fifth Sister.

873
00:40:41,560 --> 00:40:43,880
It,it's so late.

874
00:40:43,960 --> 00:40:44,720
We can't see well,

875
00:40:44,720 --> 00:40:45,470
so let's do it tomorrow.

876
00:40:45,480 --> 00:40:47,410
I'll burn a roomful of candles for you!

877
00:40:47,440 --> 00:40:48,840
Come! Talk to me for a while.

878
00:40:48,840 --> 00:40:49,320
I need to go back.

879
00:40:49,386 --> 00:40:50,040
and teach you how to woven

880
00:40:50,073 --> 00:40:51,400
It's time to sleep.

881
00:40:51,400 --> 00:40:52,100
Come on.

882
00:40:53,849 --> 00:40:55,040
Hurry and come in.

883
00:40:55,040 --> 00:40:55,480
Five sister.

884
00:40:55,480 --> 00:40:57,240
I turely see nothing.

885
00:40:58,800 --> 00:40:59,300
You...

886
00:40:59,320 --> 00:41:00,040
Sit down.

887
00:41:02,960 --> 00:41:04,040
You're acting dumb on purpose.

888
00:41:04,440 --> 00:41:05,320
Let me tell you this.

889
00:41:06,360 --> 00:41:07,840
You can't tell anyone,

890
00:41:07,840 --> 00:41:08,600
no matter who. Got it?

891
00:41:09,880 --> 00:41:10,720
Fifth Sister,

892
00:41:10,720 --> 00:41:12,400
why this fretting?

893
00:41:12,430 --> 00:41:13,800
It's no big deal anyway.

894
00:41:14,280 --> 00:41:15,440
Father wanted to find a son-in-law

895
00:41:15,440 --> 00:41:16,440
among the scholars

896
00:41:16,440 --> 00:41:17,680
for the spring exam anyway.

897
00:41:18,760 --> 00:41:20,940
So what if he finds out?

898
00:41:21,000 --> 00:41:23,400
What do you mean it's no matter?

899
00:41:26,780 --> 00:41:27,760
He...

900
00:41:29,280 --> 00:41:30,320
He isn't.

901
00:41:32,240 --> 00:41:33,240
Isn't what?

902
00:41:34,975 --> 00:41:37,240
He's not from an official's house.

903
00:41:37,320 --> 00:41:39,010
Father always devotes himself as an honest man.

904
00:41:39,080 --> 00:41:40,120
A son from a poor family

905
00:41:40,120 --> 00:41:41,320
might delight him more.

906
00:41:46,920 --> 00:41:48,280
He's Wen Yanjing.

907
00:41:49,520 --> 00:41:50,240
Who?

908
00:41:51,280 --> 00:41:52,280
Wen Yanjing.

909
00:41:55,000 --> 00:41:57,040
That's Fourth Sister's...

910
00:42:00,680 --> 00:42:01,600
He's shameless.

911
00:42:02,439 --> 00:42:03,760
He lost the match with Fourth Sister

912
00:42:03,760 --> 00:42:04,720
and he comes to bother you!

913
00:42:05,084 --> 00:42:06,560
What are you saying?

914
00:42:07,174 --> 00:42:08,240
Brother Jing

915
00:42:08,240 --> 00:42:10,220
is a complete gentleman,

916
00:42:10,320 --> 00:42:12,840
and he liked me first.

917
00:42:14,200 --> 00:42:15,520
At the time,

918
00:42:15,520 --> 00:42:16,225
Father wanted to

919
00:42:16,225 --> 00:42:17,240
pick a son-in-law for Fourth Sister.

920
00:42:17,640 --> 00:42:18,760
And he selected him

921
00:42:18,760 --> 00:42:19,520
and had him come

922
00:42:19,520 --> 00:42:21,000
and have tea at home.

923
00:42:21,770 --> 00:42:24,000
Yes, so Second Brother came back and also said

924
00:42:24,000 --> 00:42:24,760
that Scholar Wen

925
00:42:24,760 --> 00:42:26,240
is a loyal and upright man.

926
00:42:26,520 --> 00:42:27,480
And his studies are good

927
00:42:27,480 --> 00:42:28,840
and hopeful for officialdom in the future.

928
00:42:30,320 --> 00:42:31,960
It was the time

929
00:42:31,960 --> 00:42:34,090
that I lost my handkerchief in the yard.

930
00:42:34,120 --> 00:42:35,800
Brother Wen passed by,

931
00:42:35,800 --> 00:42:37,410
and thought I was a junior maidservant.

932
00:42:37,520 --> 00:42:39,240
He picked up the handkerchief for me.

933
00:42:39,800 --> 00:42:41,480
Then later,

934
00:42:41,480 --> 00:42:42,960
he came a few more times.

935
00:42:43,160 --> 00:42:45,480
Each time, I waited in the garden

936
00:42:45,480 --> 00:42:47,320
so I could talk to him.

937
00:42:49,520 --> 00:42:52,680
He said, I was pretty.

938
00:42:52,680 --> 00:42:56,320
That I'm spirited and clever.

939
00:42:56,320 --> 00:42:58,520
That I make people feel bright-hearted.

940
00:43:01,840 --> 00:43:03,400
He said that sincerely,

941
00:43:03,400 --> 00:43:04,400
or to flatter you?

942
00:43:04,760 --> 00:43:05,920
What do you know?

943
00:43:06,880 --> 00:43:07,960
Later, he found out

944
00:43:07,960 --> 00:43:09,520
I was Sheng House's legitimate daughter.

945
00:43:09,520 --> 00:43:10,160
And he also knew that

946
00:43:10,160 --> 00:43:11,025
Father wanted him to marry

947
00:43:11,025 --> 00:43:11,960
the concubine-born daughter

948
00:43:11,960 --> 00:43:13,640
so he wrote me a letter.

949
00:43:14,200 --> 00:43:16,000
He said that Father and Elder Brother

950
00:43:16,000 --> 00:43:17,360
treated him kindly in acknowledging him

951
00:43:17,360 --> 00:43:18,700
and he can't defy their grace.

952
00:43:18,760 --> 00:43:20,600
So he wouldn't ever see me again.

953
00:43:21,080 --> 00:43:22,000
Really?

954
00:43:22,000 --> 00:43:23,400
Of course it's true.

955
00:43:23,400 --> 00:43:24,600
I still have the letter now.

956
00:43:25,760 --> 00:43:28,720
At the time, I already had him in my heart.

957
00:43:28,840 --> 00:43:29,745
Whatever he says,

958
00:43:29,760 --> 00:43:31,960
I will go along.

959
00:43:31,960 --> 00:43:33,330
If he were crooked-minded,

960
00:43:33,440 --> 00:43:34,520
he could've

961
00:43:34,520 --> 00:43:35,880
just clung onto me.

962
00:43:35,880 --> 00:43:37,160
But he didn't.

963
00:43:39,760 --> 00:43:41,720
He's an upright man then.

964
00:43:43,078 --> 00:43:44,880
Where's the letter?

965
00:43:44,880 --> 00:43:45,920
Hurry and burn it.

966
00:43:46,840 --> 00:43:48,760
I can't bear to.

967
00:43:48,760 --> 00:43:50,320
I want to keep it forever.
